---
title: Mango-Glazed Jerk Chicken Tacos with Kiwi Salsa
description: Kiwi is the perfect sweet-and-sour ingredient to add a boost of flavour to standard salsa. It really amps up these Mango-Glazed Jerk Chicken Tacos!

